"- `chrome_tracing.json`: Chrome tracing format data, which can be opened in [MindStudio Insight](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/mindstudio/830/GUI_baseddevelopmenttool/msascendinsightug/Insight_userguide_0002.html?framework=mindspore).\n"
"- `profiler.db`: Performance data in database format.\n"
